d on March 11. Saturday, Feb. 25, 2017 Final deadline for applications.  Email documents to tamsadmissions@unt.edu. Saturday, March 4, 2017 Preview Day for 7th - 9th graders and families, 8:00am to 12:30pm Saturday, March 11, 2017 Early Decision admissions notifications. Saturday, March 25, 2017 Interview Day - Candidates interview and take Algebra I & II tests; invitation only. Saturday, May 6, 2017 Regular Decision admissions notifications. Fri & Sat, June 9 & 10, 2017 New student Orientation - attendance highly recommended. Contact Admissions: tamsadmissions@unt.edu Visit Us McConnell Hall 1705 W Sycamore St. Denton, TX 76201 Mail Us TAMS 1155 Union Circle #305309 Denton, TX 76203-5017 Contact Us 940-565-3606 tamsadmissions@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on May 05, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on May 05, 2017 | Important Links 